，此一竖子何足惜哉！</u>&rdquo;帝不得已，命诛之。(节选自《宋史纪事本末&middot;太宗致治》，有删改)</p><p>[注]　①富弼，北宋仁宗、神宗时的名相。文中所记是他对前代朝政的评价。②侯莫陈利用，姓侯莫陈，名利用，鲜卑人。</p>","createBy":"35988","createName":null,"createTime":"2022-06-23T07:30:30","decipherment":null,"deleted":false,"difficultyId":"10019","difficultyName":"中档题","gradeId":null,"id":"765383230558835285","isCharged":false,"isGroupQuestion":true,"isSubjective":false,"lineNumber":1,"oldId":"2609652","optionA":null,"optionB":null,"optionC":null,"optionD":null,"optionE":null,"optionF":null,"optionG":null,"options":[],"origin":1,"paperTypeId":null,"parentId":"0","pickCount":0,"provinceId":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionSerialNo":1753016,"questionVideo":null,"relateKnowledge":null,"scoreBasis":null,"source":null,"title":null,"typeDetailId":"6","typeDetailName":"简答题","typeId":"53","typeName":"文言文阅读","updateBy":"35988","updateName":null,"updateTime":"2022-06-23T07:30:30","uploadBatch":"1655969430","yearId":null},"questionId":null,"questionNumber":null},{"answer":null,"answerStatus":null,"childQuestionList":[{"answer":null,"answerStatus":6,"childQuestionList":null,"chooseGroup":null,"chooseGroupQuestionList":null,"isAnswer":false,"isChooseGroup":null,"isGroupQuestion":null,"isMistake":null,"ordered":15,"question":{"answer":"<span>C</span>","answerExplanation":"<span>&ldquo;展现了井冈山自然景物的巨大变化&rdquo;错，不仅指自然景物的变化，还指社会的巨大变革。</span>","cityId":null,"content":"<p>下列对这首词的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是(　　)</p>","createBy":"35988","createName":null,"createTime":"2022-06-23T07:30:30","decipherment":null,"deleted":false,"difficultyId":"10019","difficultyName":"中档题","gradeId":null,"id":"765383422628598407","isCharged":false,"isGroupQuestion":false,"isSubjective":false,"lineNumber":1,"oldId":"2609659","optionA":"<span>作者回到阔别三十八年的井冈山，故地重游，引发了无限感慨，表达了将革命进行到底的豪气和雄心壮志。</span>","optionB":"<span>该词上片主要描写了井冈山宏伟的景象，下片主要回忆曾经的革命战争，让读者领略到作者豪迈的风采。</span>","optionC":"<span>&ldquo;天渊翻覆&rdquo;一词，极言变化之大，与上阕的&ldquo;古代曾云海绿&rdquo;意思一致，展现了井冈山自然景物的巨大变化。</span>","optionD":"<span>&ldquo;犹记&rdquo;两句，是作者对井冈山革命斗争